   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The signing process begins when you receive an email notification from Adobe Sign as a
         signer informing you that you have a document to sign. The email notification contains a
         message from the sender and a link to open the document. To begin the signing process,
         click the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">review and sign</uicontrol> link to access the document from your
         email. Then, complete each Adobe Sign tag and add your electronic signature where required
         to sign or initial. Adding the required information in each Adobe Sign tag and then adding
         your electronic signature completes the signing process.</p>
